"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Empty Playlist...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>नवीन</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>रिक्तं प्लेलिस्ट् ...</guimenuitem> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new playlist"
msgstr "नूतनं प्लेलिस्ट् रचयन्तु"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Search Playlist...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>नवीन</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>प्लेलिस्ट् अन्वेष्टुम् ...</guimenuitem> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new <link linkend=\"juk-search-playlists\">search playlist</link>."
msgstr ""
"एकं नूतनं निर्माति<link linkend=\"juk-search-playlists\"> प्लेलिस्ट् अन्वेष्टुम्</link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Playlist From Folder...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>नवीन</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>प्लेलिस्ट् From समुच्चय...</guimenuitem> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1075
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new playlist, containing all music files in a folder and any sub-"
"folders. Any music within playlists files that &juk; recognizes will also be "
"added."
msgstr ""
"नूतनं प्लेलिस्ट् निर्माति, यत्र एकस्मिन् पुटे सर्वाणि सङ्गीतसञ्चिकाः, केचन उपपुटाः च सन्ति । "
"प्लेलिस्ट् अन्तः यत्किमपि सङ्गीतं तत् सञ्चिकां करोति यत् &juk; recognizes अपि योजितं "
"भविष्यति।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> <guimenuitem>उद्घाट्य...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a file (or files) to add to the collection list. If you select a "
"playlist file, every file in the playlist will be added."
msgstr ""
"संग्रहसूचौ योजयितुं सञ्चिकां (सञ्चिकाः वा) चिनोतु । यदि भवान् प्लेलिस्ट् सञ्चिकां चिनोति "
"तर्हि प्लेलिस्ट् मध्ये प्रत्येकं सञ्चिका योजितं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Folders...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guimenuitem>पुटं प्रबन्धयन्तु...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item opens the same window that is shown on a first &juk; start"
msgstr "एतत् मेन्यू-वस्तु तदेव विण्डो उद्घाटयति यत् प्रथमे &juk; प्रारंभः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a folder (or folders) to add to the collection list. These folders "
"will also be rescanned whenever &juk; is started or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> is chosen."
msgstr ""
"संग्रहसूचौ योजयितुं एकं पुटं (अथवा पुटं) चिनोतु । एतानि पुटानि अपि यदा कदापि &juk; आरब्धं "
"भवति अथवा <menuchoice><guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guimenuitem>पुनः लोड्</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> इति चयनं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select folders that should not be automatically searched (which "
"would override the list of folders to scan on startup). This way you can "
"avoid having to completely change up your music layout on-disk just to keep "
"&juk; from automatically grabbing songs you do not want or need managed from "
"within &juk;."
msgstr ""
"स्वयमेव अन्वेष्टुं न कर्तव्यानि पुटानि अपि चिन्वितुं शक्नुवन्ति (यत् आरम्भे स्कैन् कर्तुं पुटस्य सूचीं "
"अधिलिखति) । एवं भवन्तः केवलं &juk; &juk;"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Manage Folders dialog"
msgstr "Manage Folders इति संवादः"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Manage Folders Dialog."
msgstr "Manage Folders Dialog इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to remove files that are already in the collection list, you can "
"enable the <guilabel>File Name (full path)</guilabel> column in a playlist "
"and then use the search bar to find the offending path name, select and "
"remove the files that are shown."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् संग्रहसूचौ पूर्वमेव सन्ति सञ्चिकाः अपसारयितुम् इच्छति तर्हि भवान् प्लेलिस्ट् मध्ये "
"<guilabel>सञ्चिकानाम (पूर्णमार्गः)</guilabel> स्तम्भं सक्षमं कर्तुं शक्नोति ततः "
"अपराधमार्गनाम अन्वेष्टुं अन्वेषणपट्टिकायाः उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोति, च चिनोतु दर्शिताः सञ्चिकाः "
"निष्कासयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पुनर्नाम...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename a playlist."
msgstr "प्लेलिस्ट् इत्यस्य नाम परिवर्तनं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Duplicate...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guimenuitem>द्वितीयकं...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a duplicate of the selected playlist, and prompt for a new name."
msgstr "चयनितस्य प्लेलिस्ट् इत्यस्य द्वितीयकं रचयन्तु, नूतनं नाम च प्रार्थयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guimenuitem>पुनः लोड्</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads the tag information on every file in the selected playlist."
msgstr "चयनितप्लेलिस्ट् मध्ये प्रत्येकस्मिन् सञ्चिकायां टैग् सूचनां पुनः लोड् करोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guimenuitem>निष्कासयन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove the selected playlist."
msgstr "चयनितं प्लेलिस्ट् निष्कासयन्तु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guimenuitem>रक्षतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the selected playlist."
msgstr "चयनितं प्लेलिस्ट् रक्षन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guimenuitem>यथा रक्षतु...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the selected playlist, with a different name."
msgstr "चयनितं प्लेलिस्ट् रक्षन्तु, भिन्ननाम्ना ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Menu"
msgstr "मेनू सम्पादयतु"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सम्पादनं</guimenu><guimenuitem>साफ</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the selected songs from the playlist."
msgstr "चयनितगीतानि प्लेलिस्ट् तः निष्कासयति ।"

