#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Menu"
msgstr "मेनू देखें"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Search Bar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guimenuitem>अन्वेषणपट्टिकां दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle action that sets whether or not the <link linkend=\"search-"
"bar\">Search Bar</link> is shown."
msgstr ""
"इदं टोग्ल् क्रिया अस्ति यत् सेट् करोति यत् किं वा न वा<link linkend=\"search-bar\"> "
"अन्वेषणपट्टिका</link> इति दर्शितम् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Tag Editor</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guimenuitem>टैग् सम्पादकं दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle action that sets whether or not the <interface>Tag Editor</"
"interface> is shown."
msgstr ""
"एतत् एकं टॉग्ल् क्रिया अस्ति यत् <interface>Tag Editor</interface> दर्शितं वा न वा "
"इति सेट् करोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show History</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guimenuitem>इतिहासं दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle action that sets whether or not the <link linkend=\"juk-"
"history-playlists\">History Playlist</link> is shown."
msgstr ""
"इदं टोग्ल् क्रिया अस्ति यत् सेट् करोति यत् किं वा न वा<link linkend=\"juk-history-"
"playlists\"> इतिहास प्लेलिस्ट</link> इति दर्शितम् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Default</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>दृश्यविधानानि</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>पूर्वनिर्धारित</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switches to <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-default\">Default View mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"स्विच करोति<link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-default\"> पूर्वनिर्धारित दृश्य मोड</"
"link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Compact</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>दृश्यविधानानि</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>संकुचित</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switches to <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-compact\">Compact View mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"स्विच करोति<link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-compact\"> Compact View मोड्</link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Tree</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>दृश्यविधानानि</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>वृक्ष</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switches to <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-tree\">Tree View mode</link>."
msgstr "स्विच करोति<link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-tree\"> Tree View मोड्</link> ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player Menu"
msgstr "खिलाडी मेनू"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Random Play</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>क्रीडकः</guimenu><guimenuitem>यादृच्छिकक्रीडा</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option which controls the Random Play setting. If Random "
"Play is enabled, then &juk; will randomly select a random song from the "
"current playlist when the currently playing song is over."
msgstr ""
"इदं toggle विकल्पः अस्ति यत् Random Play सेटिंग् नियन्त्रयति । यदि Random Play सक्षमम् "
"अस्ति तर्हि &juk; वर्तमानप्लेलिस्ट् तः यादृच्छिकरूपेण यादृच्छिकं गीतं चिनोति यदा वर्तमानं "
"वाद्यमानं गीतं समाप्तं भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Loop Playlist</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>क्रीडकः</guimenu><guimenuitem>लूप् प्लेलिस्ट्</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option which controls the Loop Playlist setting. If Loop "
"Playlist is enabled, then &juk; will start playing from the beginning when "
"it has finished playing every song in the current playlist."
msgstr ""
"इदं toggle विकल्पः अस्ति यत् Loop Playlist सेटिंग् नियन्त्रयति । यदि Loop Playlist "
"सक्षमम् अस्ति तर्हि &juk; वर्तमानप्लेलिस्ट् मध्ये प्रत्येकं गीतं वादयितुं समाप्तं कृत्वा आरम्भादेव "
"वादयितुं आरभेत ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Play</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>क्रीडकः</guimenu><guimenuitem>खेल</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command starts playing the currently selected song, or resumes playback "
"of the song if it was paused."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः सम्प्रति चयनितं गीतं वादयितुं आरभते, अथवा गीतस्य वाद्यं पुनः आरभते यदि तत् "
"विरामितम् आसीत् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>क्रीडकः</guimenu><guimenuitem>विरामं कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command pauses the currently playing song. Use the Play command to "
"restart playback."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः वर्तमानकाले वाद्यमानं गीतं विरामयति । प्लेबैक् पुनः आरभ्यतुं Play आदेशस्य उपयोगं "
"कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>क्रीडकः</guimenu><guimenuitem>स्थगयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command stops the playback of the currently playing song. You cannot "
"resume playback from its current position after that."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः वर्तमानकाले वाद्यमानस्य गीतस्य वाद्यं स्थगयति । तदनन्तरं भवन्तः तस्य "
"वर्तमानस्थानात् पुनः प्लेबैक् आरभुं न शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1344
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>क्रीडकः</guimenu><guimenuitem>अनन्तरं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command skips to the next song to play in the playlist."
msgstr "एषः आदेशः प्लेलिस्ट् मध्ये वादयितुं अग्रिमगीतं प्रति लङ्घयति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>क्रीडकः</guimenu><guimenuitem>पूर्व</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command plays the song that was playing before the currently playing "
"song."
msgstr "एषः आदेशः वर्तमानं वाद्यमानस्य गीतस्य पूर्वं यत् गीतं वादयति स्म तत् वादयति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1369
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tagger Menu"
msgstr "टैग्स मेनू"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>टैगर</guimenu><guimenuitem>रक्षतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command saves any changes to the tags that you are editing. Normally, "
"changes are not saved until you deselect the file you are editing."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः भवान् यत् टैग् सम्पादयति तस्मिन् यत्किमपि परिवर्तनं रक्षति । सामान्यतया, "
"परिवर्तनं तावत्पर्यन्तं न रक्षितं भवति यावत् भवन्तः सम्पादयन्ति सञ्चिकां विचयनं न कुर्वन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1386
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>टैगर</guimenu><guimenuitem>विलोपन</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command deletes the currently selected files from the Collection List "
"and any playlists containing it, and then deletes the selected file from the "
"disk."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः वर्तमानचयनितसञ्चिकाः संग्रहसूचिकातः तत्युक्तानि कानिचन प्लेलिस्ट् च अपास्यति, "
"ततः चयनितसञ्चिकां डिस्कतः अपास्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Refresh</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>टैगर</guimenu><guimenuitem>ताजगी</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1402
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command allows you to refresh playlist tags after changing them."
msgstr "एषः आदेशः भवन्तं प्लेलिस्ट् टैग् परिवर्तनानन्तरं ताजगीं कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guisubmenu>Guess Tag Information</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>From Filename</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>टैगर</guimenu><guisubmenu>टैगसूचना अनुमानं कुरुत</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem> सञ्चिकानाम</guimenuitem>तः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command tries to guess the tags of the selected files by scanning the "
"filename. You can configure the patterns used for guessing by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tag Guesser...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, which opens the <link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-"
"configuration\">Tag Guesser Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः सञ्चिकानाम स्कैन् कृत्वा चयनितसञ्चिकानां टैग्स् अनुमानं कर्तुं प्रयतते । अनुमानार्थं "
"प्रयुक्तानि प्रतिमानाः चयनं कृत्वा विन्यस्तुं शक्नुवन्ति<menuchoice><guimenu> सेटिंग्स्</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem> टैग Guesser...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> , यत् "
"उद्घाटयति<link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-configuration\"> Tag Guesser "
"Configuration संवादः</link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guisubmenu>Guess Tag Information</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>From Internet</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>टैगर</guimenu><guisubmenu>टैगसूचनायाः अनुमानं कुरुत</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem> अन्तर्जाल</guimenuitem>तः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command tries to guess the tags of the selected files by using the "
"<application>TunePimp</application> library provided with <ulink url="
"\"http://www.musicbrainz.org/\">MusicBrainz</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः <ulink url=\"http://www.musicbrainz.org/\">MusicBrainz</ulink> "
"इत्यनेन सह प्रदत्तस्य <application>TunePimp</application> पुस्तकालयस्य उपयोगेन "
"चयनितसञ्चिकानां टैग्स् अनुमानं कर्तुं प्रयतते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Rename File</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>टैगर</guimenu><guimenuitem>सञ्चिकायाः नाम परिवर्तनं</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command allows you to rename a file or a group of files for the "
"selected songs in the playlist. Before the real rename happens &juk; will "
"show a preview dialog where you can confirm or cancel the action."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः भवन्तं प्लेलिस्ट् मध्ये चयनितगीतानां कृते सञ्चिकायाः अथवा सञ्चिकासमूहस्य नाम "
"परिवर्तयितुं शक्नोति । वास्तविकं नामकरणं भवितुं पूर्वं &juk; पूर्वावलोकनसंवादं दर्शयिष्यति यत्र "
"भवान् क्रियायाः पुष्टिं कर्तुं वा रद्दं कर्तुं वा शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The files will be renamed according to the parameters defined using <link "
"linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\">Rename File dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"उपयोगेन परिभाषितमापदण्डानुसारं सञ्चिकानां नाम परिवर्तनं भविष्यति<link linkend=\"juk-"
"rename-dialog\"> सञ्चिकासंवादस्य नाम परिवर्तनं कुर्वन्तु</link> ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Menu"
msgstr "सेटिंग्स् मेनू"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Toolbars Shown</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Main / Play Toolbar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guisubmenu>उपकरणपट्टिकाः दर्शिताः</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>मुख्य / प्ले साधनपट्टिका</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These commands show or hide the <link linkend=\"main-toolbar\">Main Toolbar</"
"link> and the <link linkend=\"play-toolbar\">Play Toolbar</link>."
msgstr ""
"एते आदेशाः दर्शयन्ति वा गोपयन्ति वा<link linkend=\"main-toolbar\"> मुख्य साधनपट्टी</"
"link> तथा<link linkend=\"play-toolbar\"> Toolbar प्ले कुर्वन्तु</link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dock in System Tray</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सिस्टम ट्रे</guimenuitem> मध्ये डॉक् कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option. If enabled, &juk; will display an icon in your "
"system tray. You can use the system tray icon to tell if &juk; is playing, "
"and control playback."
msgstr ""
"एषः टॉग्ल् विकल्पः अस्ति । यदि सक्षमम्, &juk; भवतः सिस्टम् ट्रे मध्ये एकं चिह्नं "
"प्रदर्शयिष्यति । भवान् सिस्टम् ट्रे चिह्नस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोति यत् &juk; क्रीडति, वाद्यं च "
"नियन्त्रयति।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stay in System Tray on Close</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>बन्द</guimenuitem> इत्यत्र सिस्टम् ट्रे मध्ये "
"तिष्ठन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option. If enabled, &juk; will remain running if you close "
"the main window. The <guimenuitem>Dock in System Tray</guimenuitem> option "
"must also be enabled. To quit &juk;, use the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> command from the main "
"window, or the <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem> command from the system "
"tray's context menu."
msgstr ""
"एषः टॉग्ल् विकल्पः अस्ति । यदि सक्षमम्, &juk; यदि भवान् मुख्यविण्डो पिधायति तर्हि "
"चालितः एव तिष्ठति । <guimenuitem>Dock in System Tray</guimenuitem> विकल्पः अपि "
"सक्षमः भवितुमर्हति । &juk;तः निर्गन्तुं मुख्यविण्डोतः <menuchoice><guimenu>सञ्चिका</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> आदेशस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु, "
"अथवा प्रणाल्याः <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem> आदेशस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ट्रे इत्यस्य "
"सन्दर्भमेनू ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &juk; is started up when it is set to dock in the system tray on startup "
"a simple notification will be shown (as otherwise the user may wonder why "
"&juk; window did not open up). It is possible to remove this additional "
"notification by going to <menuchoice><guimenu>Common Appearance and "
"Behavior</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Application and System Notifications</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in &systemsettings; to manage <guilabel>JuK music "
"player</guilabel> application notifications. Just uncheck <guilabel>Show a "
"message in a popup</guilabel> item for <guimenuitem>JuK running in dock "
"mode</guimenuitem>. More information on &kde; notification settings can be "
"found <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kcmnotify\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"यदि &जुक्; आरभ्यते यदा प्रारम्भे सिस्टम् ट्रे मध्ये डॉक् कर्तुं सेट् भवति तदा सरलसूचना दर्शिता "
"भविष्यति (यथा अन्यथा उपयोक्ता चिन्तयितुं शक्नोति यत् &juk; विण्डो किमर्थं न उद्घाटितम्)। "
"&systemsettings <guilabel>JuK संगीतप्लेयर</guilabel> अनुप्रयोगसूचनाः प्रबन्धयितुं । "
"केवलं <guilabel>पॉपअप</guilabel> मदं सन्देशं दर्शयतु इति <guimenuitem>JuK डॉक् मोड् "
"मध्ये चालितं</guimenuitem> कृते अनचेक् कुर्वन्तु । &kde; सूचनासेटिंग्स् <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/kcmnotify\">अत्र</ulink> द्रष्टुं शक्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Popup Track Announcement</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पॉपअप ट्रैक घोषणा</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option. If enabled, &juk; will display an indicator "
"whenever a song starts playing, with information on the artist and title, "
"and with buttons allowing you to quickly switch to a different song. The "
"Dock in System Tray option must also be enabled."
msgstr ""
"एषः टॉग्ल् विकल्पः अस्ति । यदि सक्षमम्, &juk; यदा कदापि गीतं वादयितुं आरभते तदा सूचकं "
"प्रदर्शयिष्यति, कलाकारस्य शीर्षकस्य च सूचना सह, तथा च बटनैः सह यत् भवन्तः शीघ्रं भिन्नगीते "
"स्विच् कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति Dock in System Tray विकल्पः अपि सक्षमः भवितुमर्हति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1526
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tag Guesser...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>टैग् अनुमानक...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command brings up the <link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-configuration"
"\">Tag Guesser Configuration dialog box</link>, where you can alter the "
"patterns used to guess tag information from filenames."
msgstr ""
"अयं आदेशः उपस्थापयति<link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-configuration\"> Tag "
"Guesser Configuration संवादपेटिका</link> , यत्र भवान् सञ्चिकानामभ्यः टैग्-सूचनायाः "
"अनुमानं कर्तुं प्रयुक्तानि प्रतिमानं परिवर्तयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1538
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>File Renamer...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सञ्चिकायाः पुनर्नामकरणं...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command brings up the <link linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\">File Renamer "
"Configuration dialog box</link>, where you can alter the way &juk; renames "
"files for you."
msgstr ""
"अयं आदेशः उपस्थापयति<link linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\"> File Renamer "
"Configuration संवादपेटिका</link> , यत्र भवन्तः मार्गं परिवर्तयितुं शक्नुवन्ति &amp;juk; "
"भवतः कृते सञ्चिकानां नामकरणं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &juk; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
